source: <{{%01%}}> reached the rank of Super Soldier!
<{{%01%}}> reached the rank of Bio Weapon!!

Gene Shift Auto is a GTA-style battle royale with roguelike build crafting. Loot, shoot, and adapt your build to create godlike synergies before the final fight.
Convert {{%01%}} class flasks into a regular Epic Flask (this costs {{%02%}} Uranium)
Convert {{%01%}} Full Flask into a Play Flask (this costs {{%02%}} Uranium)
You can equip the modifiers that you own into your build on the right. Whenever you win a round, two of the modifiers in your build will be randomly chosen for everyone to vote on.

If you win a round you always get {{%04%}} votes. But if someone else wins, your voting power depends on their modifiers. If you own BOTH of their modifiers you get {{%03%}} votes, if you own ONE you get {{%02%}} votes, and if you own NONE you only get {{%01%}} votes. Unlock more modifiers to improve your voting power.

You can unlock modifiers by spending {{%01%}} SHARDS when you open a flask. This gives a {{%02%}}% chance to get a legendary modifier, a {{%03%}}% chance to get an Epic or higher, and a {{%04%}}% chance to get a Rare or higher. If you hit a modifier that you already own, you'll get +{{%05%}} ENRICHED SHARDS instead. These let you buy specific legendary modifiers directly from the shop!
To get more SHARDS, level up your classes. You get +{{%01%}} shards per class level up (tip: you can level up lower level classes faster).

Earning TROPHIES in-game levels up your modifiers. Your trophies are awarded to a random modifier that you own (prioritizing modifiers played that match if possible, otherwise from your build). The winners of each match will earn bonus trophies. Common modifiers hit max level at {{%01%}} trophies, rares at {{%02%}} trophies, epics at {{%03%}} trophies, and legendaries at {{%04%}} trophies. Get the Deluxe Edition DLC to earn these trophies {{%05%}}x faster, and raise the trophy limit to {{%06%}} for all rarities.
If a class build is on, it is used when playing that class instead of the default build.

Every {{%01%}} trophies earned on a modifier will let you level it up and claim bonus ACID. Also, as your total trophy count increases, your victory screen will gain cool cosmetic effects! Unlock more modifiers and get the Deluxe Edition DLC to raise your total trophy limit.
Each round, these weekly modifiers are mixed into the winner's build, giving them a {{%01%}}% chance to appear for voting. These are added even for players who haven't unlocked them yet!
At the start of each Monday and Friday (0:00 UTC), the modifier on the right shifts into the slot on the left, and a new one appears on the right. Legendary modifiers will never appear here.
No modifier equipped. A random modifier that you own will be used when you win rounds.
No modifier equipped. A random modifier from your default build will be used.
Level this modifier up to claim +{{%01%}} ACID!
This modifier is max level. It can no longer earn trophies unless you upgrade it to premium, which raises the cap to {{%01%}}.
This premium modifier is at max level!
You earned the max of {{%01%}} trophies for this rarity!
Get the DLC to raise the max trophies to {{%01%}}. You'll also earn trophies {{%02%}}x faster!
Unlock this modifier to begin earning trophies for it.
You've earned {{%01%}} trophies. Reach {{%02%}} to level this up!
Your best kill streak with this mod is {{%01%}}.
Upgrade this to PREMIUM to show the best kill streak you got with this modifier!

Spend {{%01%}} SHARDS to drastically boost your chance of getting a new ROUND MODIFIER! If you hit a duplicate modifier you'll get +{{%02%}} ENRICHED SHARDS instead. These are used to buy specific modifiers from the shop.
Not enough SHARDS. You need at least {{%01%}} shards to unlock new round modifiers.
All modifiers unlocked! You can't spend shards until more modifiers are added to the game.

You can now equip this to your build in the MODIFIERS tab. This gives it a chance to appear for voting when you win a round.
This super challenge can be claimed for {{%01%}} Uranium, giving XP and ACID at {{%02%}}x value!
Combine FLASKS and ACID to get DNA for your skills. DNA lets you equip skills to your skill builds. Certain types of flask can also unlock brand new skills.
When using a FLASK you can also spend a MAGNET on a specific class/skill DNA combo. This adds an extra DNA drop to the flask for the chosen combo, with a chance to hit a Rare or higher!
Tip: Magnets are most effective when used with a Magnetic Flask, Legendary Flask, or Epic Flask.
Select a specific skill to level up. This makes it earn +{{%01%}} DNA in your next flask, so it reaches Legendary status faster! This costs 1 MAGNET per flask.
Right Click the flasks above to open multiple in a row. The flasks will automatically open in order until the queue ends. To cancel mid-queue, click this button between flasks.
You can spend MAGNETS to level up specific skills when you reach level {{%01%}}.
You can't use MAGNETS with this type of flask.
Enable the spending of MAGNETS to earn +{{%01%}} DNA for the skill equipped to the left. Click the button on the left to change the skill you want to level up.
You have no flasks. Level up to get more, and claim them with the button above.
Flasks purchased from the shop appear here. Unlike regular flasks, these don't require any ACID to open.
Flasks purchased from the shop, or in the purchased tab of the shop, don't require any ACID to open.
Hi veterans! Your old progress is not lost. You'll level up {{%01%}}x faster until you reach {{%02%}}xp (level {{%03%}}).

target: Позволяет менять цвет фар машины. Устройте диско-вечеринку вместе с неоновой подсветкой!

source: Burn rubber with some sweet decals on your vehicle. Flames, flowers, stripes and more.
target: Рисунки для вашей машины. Огонь, цветы, полосы. Вы можете выбрать цвет рисунка.

source: Change the color of your bullet trails. Your enemies will know they're in trouble when they see your uniquely colored bullets fly by.
target: Измените цвет следов ваших пуль! Ваши враги поймут, что у них проблемы, увидев ваши уникальные пули, летящие в их сторону. Смотрите как они разбегаются в страхе увидев пули из вашей винтовки!

source: Adds an extra cool trail effect when you fall from the sky. Use the color slider to mix and match with your smoke trails.
Wear some wings when you're a zombie. They'll flap about when you jump, but won't make you jump any higher.
Get the Deluxe Edition DLC to show the Supporter's Medallion next to your name! Like all cosmetics, this can be toggled on or off.
Upgrades the Supporter medallion shown next to your name in leaderboards and chat.
Gives your {{%01%}} a bluish silver skin, and makes it glow in the moonlight.
Gives your {{%01%}} an eye-catching golden skin, and makes it reflect a golden glow.
Gives your {{%01%}} a golden glow when it flies through the air.
Changes your hair from brown to blond.
Visually increases your power level to over 9000.
Cosplay as a survivor in the poison gas.
Blend in with the cops before you blast them away.
Gives you spiky horns when you're a zombie.
As a mercenary guards have no effect on missions. You must only target other mutants.
target: Наёмники не могут убивать гангстеров ради миссий. Чтобы получать деньги, нужно убивать мутантов.

source: This mission requires teammates and does not work as a mercenary.
target: Миссия требует союзников, она недоступна для наёмников.

source: Creates a buy zone where you're standing, with a higher chance of discounts.
Used to capture Conquest control points. Place this directly onto a control point to capture it.
Creates a supply drop at your current location.
Teleports you to other Warp Fields (you need at least 2). Stand in it, hold ALT, and click an arrow to teleport.
Gives you global vision while standing inside it and for the following {{%01%}}s.

target: Увеличивает урон от вашего оружия на

source: Allows you to destroy enemy chemicals by standing on top of them.

Protects your chemicals from enemy Neutralizers. Place this on a chemical and if an enemy tries to neutralize it, it will remove the Insulator but save the original chemical. Can only be used once per chemical.
target: Защищает ваши химикаты от Neutralizers противника. Поставьте этот химикат поверх других, и когда враг попытается его уничтожить, враг уничтожит только Insulator. Лимит 1 на химикат.

source: Reveals the location of nearby enemy chemicals making them easier to neutralize. The revealing range is
Upgrade: Makes the chemical you're standing in invisible to enemies unless they stand inside it.
Enemies in your Goo Trap will move slower.
Creates a laser that zaps enemies who walk through it. This deals {{%01%}} of their current health.
Explodes for {{%01%}} hp damage when an enemy steps inside it.
Extends your magazine by giving a free bullet every {{%01%}} shots.
Your gun's critical damage will increase by {{%01%}} when you kill an enemy player or a cop. This can go {{%02%}} higher than the default cap of {{%03%}}.
Gives +{{%01%}}% explosion size to grenades and other explosives.
This is placed into the map and is hidden from enemies unless they stand inside it.
Does not work as a zombie.
Play a random class, prioritizing daily challenges if available. Your skill build will match the selected build on that class.
Randomise your skill build but get +{{%01%}} free reroll. This can be combined with Random Class above to stack the XP bonuses.
You earn +{{%01%}}% cash and XP from all sources in-game, as it can be harder to get synergies.
Do you think the skills on class A actually work better on class B? You can completely swap ALL the skill DNA between 2 classes!

This is permanent, but you can always pay to swap back. You never lose class levels, but you might gain some. The cost is based on whichever class has more DNA (shown to the left). Cost = {{%02%}} x DNA% (capped at {{%03%}}).
Equip your favorite skills! This makes them appear more often when you level up in-game.
You need {{%01%}} DNA to reach Rare, {{%02%}} for Epic, and {{%03%}} for Legendary.

Open flasks to get higher rarities on your skills. This makes them stronger. Also, when a skill becomes legendary, you are allowed to equip it to the top 2 slots of your build. Unlike the bottom 6 skills which are random, these top 2 skills always appear (at level {{%01%}}), and let you play your favorite skill every match!

Most skills shown in-game are random. But when you hit level {{%01%}} in-game you'll see 3 skill options instead of 2. The 2 on the right will show the top 2 slots of your build here. Then at level {{%03%}} you'll also see 3 options, and the 2 on the right are chosen randomly from the bottom section of your build. The far right slot can only be claimed if you first get {{%04%}} kills.
DNA lets you equip skills to your skill builds. You need {{%03%}} DNA to equip a skill as Rare, {{%02%}} as Epic, and {{%01%}} as Legendary.
Starter flasks drop the same skills for all players.
Has a {{%01%}}% chance to unlock new skills in the 3rd ring of the skill tree.
Has a {{%01%}}% chance to unlock skills in the 3rd ring of the tree, and a {{%02%}}% chance for skills in the 4th ring.

When using a magnet with this flask, it is guaranteed to hit a good rarity and will never land on a common drop. This ensures at least {{%01%}} DNA (Rare, plus the bonus +{{%02%}} DNA magnets always give).
Always gives at least an Epic drop of {{%01%}} DNA! Has a {{%03%}}% chance of a Legendary DNA drop (instead of the usual {{%04%}}%).

Always gives a Legendary drop of {{%01%}} DNA! Also has a {{%02%}}% chance to drop a new legendary modifier (with duplicate protection!). With shards, the chance is {{%03%}}% instead of the usual {{%04%}}%. If you miss, you get a new non-duplicate Epic modifier.

Always gives at least an Epic drop of {{%01%}} DNA! This is for a randomly chosen class, shown in the description. This class randomly changes whenever you open any flask, and also at 0:00 UTC every day.
Always gives a Legendary drop of {{%01%}} DNA! This is for a randomly chosen class, shown in the description. This class randomly changes whenever you open any flask, and also at 0:00 UTC every day.
This flask only costs {{%01%}} ACID to open. However it will not drop DNA for your {{%02%}} most played classes.
All DNA drops go towards the last class you played. This class is shown in the description.
Gives bonus XP based on how much DNA is earned. This gives at least +{{%03%}} account levels per flask, or more if you hit an Epic or Legendary.
Always gives you a brand new skill from rings 3 or 4, as long as some are still locked.

Has a chance to upgrade your modifiers to Premium status! Premium modifiers look cool and display the biggest kill streak you earned with that modifier. They can also earn up to {{%01%}} trophies, which raises your trophy limit and shows a new badge.
Claiming this will give you a random special flask.
Guarantees {{%01%}} DNA drops for the {{%02%}} class.
Gives a competitive build for the {{%01%}} class!
A special flask to give newbies a competitive build. All players get the same skills from this.

Always gives a Legendary drop of {{%01%}} DNA, always for the {{%02%}} class! Also has a {{%03%}}% chance to drop a new legendary modifier (with duplicate protection). With shards the chance is {{%04%}}%. If you miss, you get a new non-duplicate Epic modifier.
Always gives at least an Epic drop of {{%01%}} DNA, always for the {{%02%}} class! Has a {{%04%}}% chance of a Legendary DNA drop (instead of the usual {{%05%}}%).
Chance of Epic DNA or Better
Chance of Rare DNA or Better
Chance Shards Give Epic Mod or Better
Chance Shards Give Rare Mod or Better
Chance Shards Give Common Mod or Better
Chance of Epic Modifier or Better
Chance of Rare Modifier or Better
Chance of Common Modifier or Better
Chance of Premium Mod (Epic or Higher)
Chance of Premium Mod (Rare or Higher)
Chance of Premium Mod (Common or Higher)
Chance Magnet Hits Epic or Better
Chance Magnet Hits Rare or Better
You'll drop a free health kit every {{%02%}} seconds. These heal you {{%01%}}% of your missing health.
Vendors sometimes sell weapons with {{%01%}} clips worth of explosive bullets. These bullets explode on impact, dealing +{{%02%}}% damage.
Restore +{{%01%}} health for each bullet that hits an enemy player, civ or cop.
Civs and cops join your gang, automatically following you and shooting at enemies. Your max gang size is {{%01%}}.
Each kill drops a health kit. This restores +{{%01%}} health, and gives your next shot +{{%02%}} damage.
Your passive regen will recharge and heal +{{%01%}}% faster whenever you stand still.
Your player and hitbox also grow bigger.
Shifts restore charges +{{%01%}}% faster when moving, or +{{%02%}}% faster when standing still.
You move +{{%01%}}% faster, and your bullets travel +{{%02%}}% faster.
Every {{%01%}} seconds there is a {{%02%}} second window where your bullets seek towards enemies and deal +{{%03%}}% damage.
You'll disguise yourself as a cop when at full health. At full health your police radio reveals nearby enemies, civs and cops.
Take {{%01%}}% damage from explosives and cars, including explosive crates and Fission Mines.
Kills during your {{%01%}}s Dagger Dance window increase the power of your upgrades by +{{%02%}}% (max +{{%03%}}%). Dying halves this bonus.
Bullets gain damage the further they travel, dealing up to +{{%01%}}% damage at {{%02%}}m. They also have +{{%03%}}% range.
Your bullets will steer towards enemies at {{%01%}} degrees per second.
Reload weapons +{{%01%}}% faster. You also won't slow down as much when firing your gun.
Gain +{{%01%}}% rate of fire for every level. When below {{%02%}}% health, this gain is +{{%03%}}% instead.
Your currently held guns gain +{{%01%}}% damage whenever you get a kill (capped at +{{%02%}}%).
Once you collect {{%01%}} items of loot, you'll duplicate all of them. Dying halves the amount collected. Doesn't duplicate ACID.
Vendor upgrades that improve skills (but not weapons) cost {{%01%}}% as much.
Your knife deals {{%01%}} instead of {{%02%}} damage.
Deal +{{%01%}}% damage vs empty vehicles. They explode with +{{%02%}}% damage and blast size.
All enemy deaths within range of your placed chemicals give you +${{%03%}} and +{{%04%}} clips worth of Ballistic Bombs in both your guns.
Whenever you throw an explosive you will throw +{{%01%}} extra for free shortly after.
Explosives reload +{{%01%}}% faster and fly +{{%02%}}% faster through the air.
Active skills have +{{%01%}}% cooldown speed. They also restore +{{%02%}} health when cast.
Chemical passive and active effects are +{{%01%}}% stronger. Chemicals are discounted, and they restore charges +{{%02%}}% faster.
Get +{{%01%}} reroll on valid skill drafts, and all rerolls are ${{%02%}} cheaper.
Gain +{{%01%}} hp/s and +{{%02%}}% move speed for the next {{%03%}}s after placing a chemical.
Move +{{%01%}}% faster for each skill on cooldown.
When you reach level {{%01%}}, your {{%02%}} highest level skills will automatically gain one level.
Tier 2 and tier 3 guns can be purchased a round earlier, and are always discounted.
Whenever you shift, there is a {{%01%}}% chance to summon a gangster to your gang (max of {{%02%}}).
After completing a civilian mission, your next kill gives you +1 random vendor upgrade.
When chaining multi-kills you get {{%01%}}s between kills instead of {{%02%}}s.
Your Survivor Income increases +{{%01%}}% faster, and pays an additional +{{%02%}}% vs survivors.
Your Survivor Income loses {{%01%}}% when you die instead of {{%02%}}%.
The time between cop waves is reduced by {{%01%}}%. Killing cops restores +{{%02%}} health.
You will gain {{%01%}} health per second for every point in the Physical tree.
You will regenerate shifts {{%01%}}% faster for every point in the Mental tree.
You will deal {{%01%}}% more bullet damage for every point in the Cybernetic tree.
You can take a skill up to level 3 once you've spent {{%01%}} points in its skill tree.
Creates a toxic puddle on the ground wherever you get a kill or destroy a car.
Gives more cash and xp from killing players and cops. Especially at high wanted levels.
Deal extra damage vs vehicles, and vehicle explosions deal more damage. Also gain bonus cash for destroying cars.
Restores health by a percentage of the damage you deal to enemies.
Restores your health when not shooting.
Creates a shield that blocks enemy bullets and bounces them back at enemies.
Makes you invisible. You'll be revealed if you stand near an enemy, and you'll briefly deal less damage when Invis ends.
Slows the speed of all bullets in a circle around you. Any bullets you fire within Bullet Time will steer towards enemies.
Increases rate of fire and movement speed.
Creates deadly blades that spin around and slash nearby enemies. Cast again to burst them out for extra damage.
Emits a shockwave that freezes bullets in mid air, healing you for each bullet frozen. It also reveals enemies.
Launches a long range nuke that creates a radioactive field and damages enemies.
Fires {{%01%}} darts that poison enemies over time.
Launches a stream of explosive fire balls that gains damage the further they travel.
Protects you when you shift or cast skills.
Your bullets deal extra damage after shifting.
Swap between weapons and grenades faster. Explosives also fly faster through the air.
Makes you run faster when out of combat.
Creates a spinning vortex on the ground that slows enemies. You will damage enemies and steal health from each enemy caught inside it.
Increases your bullet speed and accuracy.
Makes you move faster but with less control. If you hit max speed you will glow red and deal extra weapon damage. Cast again to toggle off.
Shows nearby enemies and loot behind walls.
Makes your bullets bounce off walls.
Hypnotizes nearby civs and cops to follow you and shoot enemies. Each cast restores your followers' health.
Throws a line of spikes that damage enemies. Spikes also injure enemies, making them vulnerable to gun damage for a short time.
Grenades, bazookas and molotovs deal more damage. Grenades also drop from crates.
Instantly protects you when you're hit by an enemy. After triggering it must recharge.
Throws a smoke bomb on the ground that heals you and makes you invisible.
Protects you at low health. Any damage blocked is added to your next bullet.
Both of your guns gain seeking bullets, that accumulate in their magazines over time.
Marks your position with an X on the ground. If you cast again, you'll teleport back to this location and restore lost health.
Speeds up your skill cooldowns, chemical cooldowns, and restores your ammo whenever you kill an enemy player, civ or cop.
Adds high damage bullets to both of your guns. These bullets accumulate over time, but only when standing nearby enemy players.
Your bullets set enemies on fire.
Throws a free Molotov whenever you cast a skill or empty your magazine.
Increases all forms of non-bullet damage (skills, grenades, cars, knife). If you get a non-bullet kill, you'll gain charges that increase this damage. Charges reset on death.
Creates a clone of yourself that damages and confuses enemies. This clone moves towards your crosshair when cast.
After you cast a skill or throw a grenade, the next bullet you shoot will deal extra damage.
A random enemy will be revealed to you in the map, and you will deal bonus damage against them. If you kill them you'll earn extra cash and XP, then get a new target.
Spawns grenades that spin around you and are randomly tossed at nearby enemies.
Restores your health whenever you fall from a height. When you land on the ground, you'll deal damage to all nearby enemies.
Increases your size and max health.
Gives more shift charges and increases shift distance.
Double Damage loot will drop from enemies after you damage a percentage of their max health. After triggering it must recharge.
Deal extra damage to enemies when they have low health.
Restores your health whenever you shift.
Gives more time to chain multi-kills. The default time is {{%01%}}s. Your kills also drop free loot, dropping more at higher multi-kill levels.
Collecting loot restores your health, and shooting crates causes their loot to fly towards you.
Your vehicles drive faster, heal you, and deal extra collision damage. If you kill a player from inside a car, the heal will continue to work outside vehicles, and lasts until you die.
Killing vendors sometimes drops rare loot.
You can throw your knife at long range.
You leave a trail of poison wherever you walk, damaging enemies who step in it.
Bazookas spin around you and fire back at enemies who shoot you.
More cash and XP from kills.
Fireballs do extra damage at range.
Creates vortex that slows and damages.
Creates a line of spikes on ground.
Smoke makes you invisible and heal.
Marks spot, then teleports back to it.
Kills refresh ammo and skill cooldowns.
Gain damage charges while near enemies.
Throws a molotov on skill cast.
After skill cast, next bullet is deadly.
Kill assigned target for extra XP.
Falling heals you and harms enemies.
Extra damage vs low hp enemies.
Gives your car speed and regen.
Pretty awful as a car. But it's cheap and makes a nice step for jumping over walls.
target: Медленная и хрупкая. Плохая, но дешёвая машина хорошо подходит в качестве баррикады для зомби, или в качестве ступеньки, чтобы забраться на высокую точку.

source: Fast and agile - just watch out for the low health. If it catches on fire you'll burn.
target: Быстрая, маневренная, дешёвая. Хороша для разведки. Очень мало здоровья, если начнёт гореть - выбирайтесь как можно быстрее.

source: Fast and durable - a great all-rounder. Can survive a direct shot from a Bazooka.
target: Быстрая и крепкая, золотая середина. Может выдержать прямое попадание из базуки!

source: A good combat vehicle great for co-op drivebys. Press [F3] to hop into the back and shoot.
target: Хорошая боевая машина для целой команды. Нажмите 3, чтобы сесть на заднее сиденье с возможностью стрелять в любую сторону.

source: Has a radar that sees through walls and reveals the location of nearby enemies.
target: Оснащена радаром, который показывает ближайших противников на карте. Позволяет следить за противником сквозь стены!

source: Very durable for its price and with 6 seats it's great for transporting your squad.
target: Очень прочная для своей цены. 4 сиденья делает её очень хорошей для командного нападения. Чем больше людей внутри, тем быстрее регенерирует машина!

source: Fastest car in the game. Hold [SHIFT] to boost and scoop up all the loot in the map.
target: Самый быстрый автомобиль в игре!Венец украинского автопрома.

source: Comes with a ticking time bomb. [LEFT CLICK] to toggle the timer on and off.
target: Оснащена бомбой с часовым механизмом. ЛКМ включает и выключает таймер, не забудьте выпрыгнуть до взрыва!

source: A huge truck with massive health and 5 passenger seats. The back 3 seats allow for drivebys.
target: Огромный грузовик с огромным здоровьем. 3 задних сиденья позволяют вести стрельбу на 360 градусов. Очень дорогая, с командой её почти не остановить!

source: Fires 2 homing missiles that deal extra damage against vehicles. [LEFT CLICK] to fire.
target: Выстреливает 2 мощные ракеты, которые наводятся на игроков, машины, и зомби. Быстрая, маневренная и крепкая. Очень дорогая, но в правильных руках может очень многое.

source: Drive the Extraction Truck to its extraction zone.
target: Грузовик нужно доставить в зону доставки в режиме Extraction.

source: [LEFT CLICK] to fire a smoking hot Flamethrower. The Polytruck's windows are shatterproof.
[LEFT CLICK] to turn on the siren and scare off gangsters up to no good.
The SWAT van has more health, more aggression, and carries more baddies (well, technically goodies).
Silent and deadly. Great for finishing enemies off at close range.
Kaboom! Deals more damage the closer it lands to your enemies.
target: Граната наносит дополнительный урон зомби. Если граната взорвётся рядом с охранником, то он отвлечётся на взрыв.

source: Explodes with a huge flash of light that blinds nearby enemies.
target: Взрывается со вспышкой света и ослепляет врагов. Отвернитесь от взрыва чтобы самому не попасть под эффект.

source: Fires a homing missile that deals huge damage against vehicles.
target: Выстреливает ракету, которая наносит большой урон транспорту и зомби. Взрыв отвлекает охранников.

source: Pistols can swap between weapons faster.
Does extra damage vs civs and cops. Pistols let you swap between weapons faster.
target: Высокий урон и скорость стрельбы делают этот пистолет хорошим дополнительным оружием. Как и у всех пистолетов, пули не теряют урон при движении.

source: An extremely mobile superweapon that fires bullets that slow civs and cops. Pistols let you swap between weapons faster.
target: Экстримальное мобильное супероружие, которое замедляет врага.

source: Light weight so you move quickly while firing.
A high rof and high movement speed make this a great all-round weapon.
target: Слабая отдача и большая скорость передвижения, всесторонне хорошее оружие. Лучше всего работает на средних дистанциях, на которых можно точно стрелять в движении.

source: An extremely high damage superweapon. Its bullets pierce through enemies.
Does huge damage at point blank range.
target: Наносит огромный урон на ближней дистанции. Одного выстрела вплотную достаточно для убийства. Наносит мало урона на расстоянии.

source: An auto-shotgun with huge close range DPS.
target: Автоматический дробовик с высоким уроном и скоростью стрельбы, наносит огромный урон в секунду. Лучше всего работает на ближних дистанциях.

source: A powerful superweapon that fires explosive bullets and can blast jump you into the air.
Fast and accurate bullets make this effective at range, but the accuracy is awful while shifting.
Accurate and great at range. Fires in short bursts of 4 bullets.
An extremely accurate superweapon that fires seeking bullets.
target: Очень точное супероружие, стреляющее наводящимися пулями. Закрепившись на враге, пули начнут наводиться на него, нанося много урона при попадании.

source: Deals big damage, especially against vehicles. But you'll move slowly while firing and have awful accuracy.
Deals huge damage at extra long range.
target: Большой магазин и большой урон, особенно против транспорта. Тяжелое и медленное оружие. Активируйте барьер (CTRL), чтобы стрелять точнее.

source: An extremely high damage superweapon that deals extra damage against vehicles.
target: Чрезвычайно мощное оружие, делающее тысячи выстрелов в минуту.

source: A sniper with an extended scope lets you see enemies further away.
target: Дает вам расширенную область, чтобы видеть дальше и стрелять врагов за экраном.

source: Fires extremely fast and deadly bullets and with a scope for long range sniping.
target: Классическая снайперская винтовка. Очень большая дальность обзора, скорость пули и точность. Наносит больше урона на больших дистанциях и способна убить одним выстрелом.

source: A deadly superweapon that fires a beam of photons. Its bullets pierce through enemies.
target: Очень дальнобойное супероружие, выстреливающее луч фотонов, пробивающий игроков, навыки и барьер. Абсолютная снайперская винтовка.

source: Tosses a flaming bottle that explodes on impact and deals damage over time.
Fires a flare that explodes on impact. Good for shooting enemies behind cover. Pistols let you swap between weapons faster.
Shoots deadly fire that passes through enemies, vehicles and defensive skills.
Aww man, you got blood on my shirt.
Nearby allies support you by slowly regenerating your mana and health.
target: Ближайшие союзники помогают вам, медленно регенерируя ману и здоровье.
Наведите сюда, чтобы посмотреть меню навыков.

source: Left click skills to add them. Right click to view them.
Click 'Start Adding Skills' to create a skill build.
Win 4 HEARTS before the round ends to revive! The timer is top left.
Make sure you revive before overtime! It begins in {{%01%}}.
If you die during overtime, get hearts by killing zombies.
Hold ({{%01%}}) to send a quick message, or press ({{%02%}}) to chat.
Kill enemies to earn XP and level up.
Enter a car with ({{%01%}}), then kill a cop. You can shoot out the window when your car isn't moving.
Hold ({{%01%}}) and click 'Reset Skill Build' from the drop-down skills menu up the top of the screen.
While holding ({{%01%}}), select the skill at the top of the screen!
Press ({{%01%}}) to cast. The cooldown is shown below, use it wisely!
This is the Outbreak game mode. To win you need to kill zombies, collect their souls and return them to the bomb.
target: Это режим Outbreak. Для того, чтобы победить, нужно убивать зомби, собирать их души, и возвращать души к бомбе пока она не взорвётся. Используйте навыки с большим уроном по площади. Таким образом вы будете убивать зомби быстрее.

source: After collecting souls you need to return them to the bomb. Follow the arrow on your screen to take your souls to the bomb. Hold (TAB) to see scores.
Up the top right you'll see your 'Survivor Income'. This cash and XP is given on your next kill, and only grows when alive.
Escape the blue circle in the map. It will chase you, so use a car ({{%01%}}) and boost ({{%02%}}) to go fast!
Kill enemies during overtime to earn bonus score. Good luck!
If you don't reach the final 5, all good! You can keep looting to level up for next round.
Chemicals give you permanent passive benefits. Find a vendor and buy a FISSION MINE chemical.
Place your 'Fission Mine' with ({{%01%}}). This creates a hidden bomb in the map. This uses a charge, which restores over time. Chemical charges are shown above the weapons on the right.
Stand inside your shop and buy something. You can place shops as long as you have charges.
Pick up your chemical by standing in it and pressing ({{%01%}}).
In Conquest you need to capture all of the Control Points in the map.
Capture a point by standing next to it. The more allies nearby, the faster you will capture.
This is the Extraction game mode. Follow the white arrow on your screen to capture the enemy flag.
target: Это режим Extraction. Для победы нужно захватывать цели (Флаг, Радио и Грузовик) и переносить их в зону доставки. Следуйте за белой стрелкой для захвата цели.

source: Follow the arrow and take the flag to the enemy flag near your spawn. Hold (TAB) to see scores.
This is the Checkpoint game mode. To win you need do laps with the Battery in a vehicle. Grab a car, then follow the white arrow on your screen to pick up the Battery.
target: Это режим Checkpoint. Для победы нужно подобрать батарею машиной и проехать по кругу через контрольные пункты. Купите машину и следуйте за белой стрелкой, чтобы захватить батарею.

source: Follow the white arrow on your screen to drive the battery through each of the checkpoints. Hold (TAB) to see scores.
Stand inside an enemy chemical, hold ({{%01%}}), and select 'Neutralize Chemicals' to destroy it.
Press (F10) to finish this tutorial. This opens the How to Play Guide if you want to learn more.
Get more skills and prepare for the final fight! Overtime begins in {{%01%}}.
Try become the last man standing! There are {{%01%}} players left.
Be the last man standing to finish the tutorial!
Tip: Remember to level up your skills.
Tip: Stay out of combat to restore your health.
Tip: Try to reload after each kill.
Follow the vendor arrow, hold ({{%01%}}), and upgrade your gun.
Press ({{%01%}}) to shift behind cover and restore health.
To win the game, win round 3. Buy a MINIGUN and prepare to fight!
The cops are coming! Press ({{%01%}}) to dodge their bullets.
The cops are coming! Right Click to dodge their bullets.
A full game has 3 rounds, but you only need to win the FINAL round. Use earlier rounds to level up and prepare. Good luck!
Kill enemies in red to level up!
Find a civilian with a blue text bubble and press ({{%01%}}).
Missions are shown above the map. Do them to level up faster!
Learn to play and earn bonus XP!
target: Научитесь играть с помощью этого обучения! Вы будете получать опыт за каждый выполненный шаг!

source: The player count, timer, and your score are shown here.
Your health, lives and shifts are shown down here.
Press Q to switch weapons, and middle mouse to throw grenades.
Press 1, 2, 3 to cast skills. Hold ALT to spend skill points.
to toggle this guide on and off.

The meaning of life, the universe and everything you need to know about Gene Shift Auto can be found in this guide; so toggle this back on when you're ready to play like a pro. Until then you can press ENTER to chat with the server and ask questions. Have fun!
target: Смысл жизни, вселенной и Gene Shift Auto описан в этом руководстве; включите его, когда будете готовы играть, как профи. Пока что можете нажать ENTER и пообщаться в чате. Удачи!

source: I JUST WANT TO STOP DYING!!
EARN A LITTLE EXTRA ON THE SIDE..
What do I have to do?
Follow the arrow on your screen to reach the next checkpoint. Try to earn combo kills to gain extra cash.
What if I miss some text?
target: What if I miss some text?

source: Press (ENTER) to bring up the chat log. The green lines have important tips. Also when playing singleplayer you can hold (ALT) to pause the game and read the text at your own pace.
target: Нажмите (ENTER) чтобы просмотреть чат. Зелёным отмечены полезные советы. В одиночной игре можно удерживать (ALT), чтобы приостановить игру и прочитать текст.

source: Stay out of combat for a few seconds to trigger auto-heal. Use vehicles for protection while looting. Unlock healing skills with (ALT). Buy expensive weapons to deal extra damage.
target: Оставайтесь вне боя на короткое время, чтобы исцелиться. Купите оружие (B), стоя внутри круглого контрольно-пропускного пункта. Наконец, разблокируйте лечебные навыки (ALT) и разыграйте их с помощью правого клика, C и Z.

source: To win, simply be the last man standing on the final round. The best way to do this is to earn cash and XP in the earlier rounds to become as strong as possible.
Kill civilians and players to earn cash and XP. Unlock healing skills and buy a tier 2 gun as soon as possible. If you become a zombie, head towards a heart crate to try revive.
target: Избегайте круга смерти и попытайтесь остаться в живых. Если вы умерли и стали зомби используйте это как возможность найти деньги и химикаты. Телепортируйтесь с помощью Warp Field.

source: When you view the skills page through the main menu you're looking at your permanent skill build. This build is only used in permanent multiplayer servers and persists between rounds. This build is not used in quickmatches or the campaign.
target: В главном меню игры вы видите ваш постоянный билд. Этот билд используется только на постоянных серверах и остаётся между раундами. Не используется в quickmatch или кампании.

source: DLC owners can host their own legacy game modes and play against bots. To play against humans it's better to join an official server.
target: Скорее всего, вам это не нужно. Вы можете присоединитсья к официальному серверу или сыграть в кампанию, один или с друзьями!.

source: This saves your current arrangement of equipped skills and perks. You can also toggle off skills with the button in the bottom right.
target: Это сохранит ваше текущее расположение экипированных навыков и привилегий. Вы также можете отключить навыки с помощью кнопки в правом нижнем углу.

source: Don't make your build too small. Bigger skill builds have a higher chance for your skills to get bonus points and start at level 2.
Free accounts can only save {{%01%}} builds at a time. Delete an existing build, or get the DLC to create as many builds as you want!
target: Free accounts can only save {{%01%}} builds at a time. Delete an existing build, or get the DLC to create as many builds as you want!

source: You can improve your FPS by updating your graphics drivers. For now, would you like Gene Shift Auto to optimise your graphics settings?
target: Вы можете улучшить FPS обновив драйверы видеокарты. Вы хотите чтобы Gene Shift Auto оптимизировал ваши настройки?
Получение информации об обновлении с версии

source: Could not detect Steam. Please restart Steam to fix, or get support in Discord.
TIP: Want to get onto a rooftop? Stand on a car and blow it up to launch into the sky.
target: СОВЕТ: Хотите забраться на крышу? Встаньте на машину и взорвите ее, чтобы запустить себя в небо.

source: TIP: During overtime, heart crates drop less often. Be alive when the timer hits 0:00.
TIP: Vote for round modifiers that synergize with your class or skill build.
TIP: When using a jumppad, you can cancel your motion in mid-air by shifting.
target: СОВЕТ: При использовании трамплина вы можете отменить свое движение в воздухе, спешивсь.

source: TIP: During overtime, stick to the edge of the shrinking circle to stay alive.
TIP: Tier 2 guns become available in round 2, and tier 3 guns appear in round 3.
TIP: Use vehicles to loot the map faster and reach supply drops before they land.
TIP: Pre-place chemicals in the showdown area ahead of time to get a hidden advantage.
TIP: Stock up grenades before the final showdown, they're great for busting cover.
target: СОВЕТ: Запаситесь гранатами перед финальной схваткой, они отлично подходят для прорыва укрытия.

source: TIP: Get multi-kills vs cops and kill streaks vs players to farm faster.
target: СОВЕТ: Убивайте гражданских и копов, чтобы быстрее получать наличные и опыт.

source: TIP: You'll unlock Shards faster by playing multiple classes, instead of just one.
TIP: Click the Reroll button when drafting to see new skills and create better combos.
TIP: Create class-specific modifier builds that synergize with that class perks.
THE REST OF THIS FILE IS FROM THE SINGLEPLAYER CAMPAIGN.
target: ОСТАЛЬНАЯ ЧАСТЬ ЭТОГО ФАЙЛА ВЗЯТА ИЗ ОДИНОЧНОЙ КАМПАНИИ.
